                      <item xml:id="a2"><desc type="GuestText"><locus target="#40r #40v" facs="042 043"/>Calculation of the Feasts, Ḥäsabä Bäʿalat, <foreign xml:lang="gez">ሐሳበ፡ በዐላት፡</foreign></desc></item>
